message.content: It is difficult to provide an accurate summary of what most women in Sao Tome and Principe think of abortion as opinions on this topic can vary among individuals. As a result, there may be a significant portion of women who hold conservative views and are against abortion. However, there may also be women who support a woman's right to choose and believe in the importance of safe and legal access to abortion.
